      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense, thanks for clarifying the mechanics. One thing the manual mentioned was the importance of keeping the tube clear of obstructions. What kind of things usually cause blockages in the pitot tube, and how does an obstruction actually affect the reading on the instrument?",
